<h2>
  Modelos
</h2>
<div class="models">
  <ul>
    <li>
      <h3>Category</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>El modelo "Category" consiste de:</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>id</strong> tipo <span class="value-nmbr">number</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>name</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>imageUrl</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <pre>
{
  <span class="key">"id"</span>: <span class="value-nmbr">1</span>,
  <span class="key">"name"</span>: <span class="value-str">"aperitivos"</span>,
  <span class="key">"imageUrl"</span>: <span class="value-str">"https://images.pexels.com/photos/4109910/pexels-photo-4109910.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=750&w=1260"</span>
}
      </pre>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Product</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>El modelo "Product" consiste de:
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>id</strong> tipo <span class="value-nmbr">number</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>brand</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>productName</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>imageUrl</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span> or <span class="value-null">null</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>price</strong> tipo <span class="value-nmbr">number</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>categoryId</strong> tipo <span class="value-nmbr">number</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><em>*A tener en cuenta que no todos los productos tienen un valor para la propiedad "imageUrl", puede tener
              un valor <span class="value-null">null</span></em></p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <pre>
{
  <span class="key">"id"</span>: <span class="value-nmbr">1</span>,
  <span class="key">"brand"</span>: <span class="value-str">"Hacendado"</span>,
  <span class="key">"productName"</span>: <span class="value-str">"Nuez mondada natural"</span>
  <span class="key">"imageUrl"</span>: <span class="value-str">"https://a0.soysuper.com/beee7db9a319548510525c1329c65522.340.340.0.min.wmark.9a72b730.jpg</span>
  <span class="key">"price"</span>: <span class="value-nmbr">2.61</span>,
  <span class="key">"categoryId"</span>: <span class="value-nmbr">1</span>,
  
}
      </pre>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Pages</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>Paginated searchs contain:
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>products</strong> tipo <span class="value-product">Products Array</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>maxPages</strong> tipo <span class="value-nmbr">number</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>page</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>nextPage</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span> o <span class="value-null">null</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>prevPage</strong> tipo <span class="value-str">string</span></span> o <span
            class="value-null">null</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <em>*Las propiedades <span class="value-str">nextPage</span> y <span class="value-str">prevPage</span>
              contienen la url de la página siguiente y anterior, si no hay url disponible tendrá un valor de <span class="value-null">null</span>
            </em>
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <pre>
{
  <span class="key">"products"</span>: <span class="value-product">[ ... ]</span>,
  <span class="key">"maxPages"</span>: <span class="value-nmbr">219</span>,
  <span class="key">"page"</span>: <span class="value-str">"1"</span>
  <span class="key">"nextPage"</span>: <span class="value-str">"http://codinglights-supermarket-api.herokuapp.com/products/page/2"</span>
  <span class="key">"prevPage"</span>: <span class="value-null">null</span>
}
      </pre>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>

